These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
4 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, goldfish, hedgehog
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Pet      | goldfish  | pony | hedgehog        | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, 7up, juice
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Beverage   | sprite   | juice | 7up | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dunhill, aristoff, chaman
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##7
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Cigar   | aristoff | tiparillo  | chaman   | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, fish, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | frog   | fish | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, train, bus
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the taxi##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport         | train | taxi   | bus | quad-bike |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

