.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, car, quad-bike
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, spanish
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the car##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Transport          | quad-bike    | motorbike   | trike | car  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

