.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, lilac, ebony, black
1. the argentine is not the person who likes black##6
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
3. the spanish is the person who likes ebony##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
7. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Color           | ebony   | black    | purple       | lilac  |

