.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, scientist, security-guard
City: boston, venice, hannover, prague
1. the engineer is not the person traveling to boston##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the police-officer##7
6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| City   | prague         | hannover      | boston | venice            |

