.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, october, june
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who's birthday is in june##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
3. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Birthday           | april    | july   | june  | october      |

