.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-12::.
City: prague, venice, hamburg, colone
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person traveling to colone##6
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to venice##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| City   | venice | prague | hamburg | colone |
| Sport   | tennis  | sailing    | climbing    | skiing  |

