.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, fishing, hiking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| Beverage   | milk   | hot-chocolate      | iced-tea        | lemonade  |

