2. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
3. the italian is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the italian##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the chinese and the colombian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
