3. the mechanic is on the right of the architect##1
4. the engineer is somewhere between the coach and the person who likes ivory##7
5. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person who likes mauve and the architect##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Job           | architect | mechanic | engineer | coach  |
| Color   | ivory     | lilac   | mauve    | orange |

