.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, polish, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, train
1. the australian is somewhere between the polish and the argentine##7
2. the japanese is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the train##2
3. the polish is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
5. the australian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
6. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
