.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, board-games, baking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, documentary, drama, horror
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person watching documentary movies##6
4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby           | board-games | baking  | chess  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | horror | documentary | drama   |

