2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | time-travel | epic      | action |
| Sport     | snowboarding  | weightlifting  | tennis | climbing   |

