.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, romance, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person watching sports movies##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre         | sports    | romance | scientific     | adventure |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 